Thomas Masson "Tom" Moody (born 2 October 1965) is an Australian cricket coach,
commentator and former international cricketer.
He is currently the coach for the IPL team Sunrisers Hyderabad.
He has been appointed head coach of the Bangladesh Premier League franchise Rangpur 
Riders for the next three seasons of the tournament from 2017
as well as the head coach of the Multan Sultans in the PSL starting from 2018.
In 2017, he applied for the Head coach of Indian Cricket Team.